   "html": "1835 － 1901"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "name"
   },
   "html": "\n[ ふくざわ・ゆきち ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n慶応義塾塾長、明六社社員、適塾塾長、中津藩士、幕臣"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"06h.html\">一覧　（ハ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=blended%26keyword=%25E7%25A6%258F%25E6%25B2%25A2%2520%25E8%25AB%25AD%25E5%2590%2589\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　大阪府出身。中津藩蔵屋敷で生まれる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　長崎に蘭学修業に出、また、大坂の緒方洪庵塾に入門。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　藩命で江戸中津藩屋敷に蘭学塾を開く。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　横浜に遊び蘭学の無力を痛感、英学に転向。咸臨丸に艦長の従僕として乗り込み渡米。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　幕府遣欧使節団の探索方としてヨーロッパ６ヵ国を歴訪。のち幕臣。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　「西洋事情」を執筆、刊行。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　家塾を改革、慶応義塾と称し、「商工農士の差別なく」洋学に志す者の学習の場とする。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　「学問のすゝめ」を刊行し、総発行部数340万部の大ベストセラーとなる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　明六社に参加、「明六雑誌」などで文明開化の啓蒙活動を展開。「文明論之概略」を刊行。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　「脱亜論」を発表、アジア諸国を犠牲にしても日本が欧米列強に伍していく道を選ぶ。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
